item.title: Imperial Octopush battle it out in Oxford
item.author: Benjamin Slater,
item.description: On Saturday 30th November, the Octopush team (also known as Underwater Hockey or UWH) played their first competition of the year at the University of Oxford. For the few people reading this who don’t already know, Octopush is a game created in 1954 by scuba divers to help them let off some steam …
